STATE of North Carolina
v.
David FELTON. No. 393P03-4. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Nifong, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 27th day of July 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of October 2005."
